        fieldMask - The fields that should be serialized (even if they have empty values). If the containing message object has a non-null fieldmask, then all the fields in the field mask (and only those fields in the field mask) will be serialized. If the containing object does not have a fieldmask, then only non-empty fields will be serialized.
